            "tooltip": {
              "expr": {
                "Literal": {
                  "Value": "'The map shows the normalised cost for a biorefinery  in each municipality in mainland Portugal, according to the selections made in the municipality and CHP filters. The municipalities are coloured in shades of blue, with the lightest blue representing municipalities with the lowest normalised cost in €/Nm3 and the darkest blue representing municipalities with the highest cost. It is possible to filter a specific municipality by selecting its geographical boundary on the map. If you wish to select a municipality in the respective filter, you must click on an area of the map outside the geographical boundary of mainland Portugal in order to clear the selection made on the map.'"
                }
